1. Purpose

This document defines the official Offline-First Synchronization Architecture for the Jewellery ERP platform.

The application must remain fully operational when:

* Internet is unavailable
* Internet is unstable
* Network is slow
* Backend is temporarily unavailable

The sync engine guarantees eventual consistency between mobile devices and the central server.

